`@Todo`: Feature Support

- Command Execution (Support for all linux commands using `execvp`)

- Support for builit in commands such as (`cd`, `exit`, `help`)

- Command history cycling

- Command autocompletion and suggestions (`possibly with AI` or any other solution)

- Scripting support

- Support for `piping` (|) and `redirecting` (<>) processes

- Support for `envs`

- Prompt customization with `rc` files

- Signal Handling (`SIGINT` and `SIGTERM`)
